Description: Boris Svirsky is a successful entrepreneur and the founder of Safeway Moving, a rapidly growing moving company
Headquarters Regions: Greater Miami Area, East Coast, Southern US
Full Description: In 2010, Boris graduated from Baruch College with an undergraduate degree, but instead of pursuing a traditional career path, he decided to continue working in his family's moving company, determined to build something of his own. After years of hard work and dedication, Boris founded Safeway Moving in July 2020, intending to provide customers with a transparent and stress-free moving experience. Under Boris's leadership, Safeway Moving has achieved tremendous success within a short period of time. In January 2021, the company was listed as a top mover on movebuddha.com, a reputable website that helps consumers find reliable moving services. This was followed by another recognition on move.org in March 2021, cementing Safeway Moving's position as one of the best moving companies in the industry. Safeway Moving's growth trajectory has been impressive, with the company expanding its operations to different parts of the country. In May 2021, the company purchased its third truck, and by December 2021, it had acquired its first tractor. In February 2022, Safeway Moving became the Top Company on movebuddha.com, a testament to the company's commitment to excellence and customer satisfaction. With its exceptional service and transparent pricing, Safeway Moving has won the trust and loyalty of many customers, leading to its rapid growth and expansion. In November 2022, the company opened its doors in Florida, and by December 2022, it had expanded its operations to Dallas, TX. In January 2023, Safeway Moving further expanded its reach by opening offices in Chicago, IL, New Chicago, Indiana, and Los Angeles, CA. Despite its rapid growth, Safeway Moving has maintained its focus on providing excellent service and value to its customers. The company's commitment to transparency and fair pricing has earned it a reputation as one of the most trustworthy moving companies in the country. By doing good work and putting the customer first, Boris and his team have established Safeway Moving as a force to be reckoned with in the industry. Boris's success is a testament to his determination, hard work, and passion for the moving industry. He has proven that with the right mindset and approach, it is possible to build a successful business even in a highly competitive industry. As Safeway Moving continues to grow and expand, it is clear that Boris's entrepreneurial spirit and dedication to excellence will continue to drive the company's success for years to come. For more info log on to: https://safewaymovinginc.com/
